# CSV & Storage Rules

## Generation & Security

- CSVs must be generated server-side after payment confirmation.
- Files must be uploaded to **Cloud Storage** (S3/GCS) with restricted access.
- Provide users with a **Secure/Signed Download Link**, not a public URL.

## Data Retention

- Ensure the purchase history allows for re-downloading existing files without re-triggering the Data Axle API.
